      <title>中国停止销售与离岸地方政府融资平台债务相关的衍生品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/china-halts-sale-of-derivatives-linked-to-offshore-lgfv-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国已采取进一步措施限制国内投资者对地方政府融资平台发行的境外债务的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/china-halts-sale-of-derivatives-linked-to-offshore-lgfv-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
