      <title>财务主管表示，比索下跌还不会刺激菲律宾加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/peso-fall-won-t-spur-philippine-rate-hike-yet-finance-head-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长拉尔夫·雷克托表示，菲律宾比索目前的暴跌不太可能促使央行将关键利率从 17 年来的高点上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/peso-fall-won-t-spur-philippine-rate-hike-yet-finance-head-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:34:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行会议开始，日元逼近干预点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/yen-inches-closer-to-intervention-point-as-boj-meeting-starts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元交易者正在为 2022 年 9 月的回归做好准备，届时日本将在央行决定重申宽松货币政策后干预市场以支撑陷入困境的货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/yen-inches-closer-to-intervention-point-as-boj-meeting-starts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>VinFast 创始人承诺投资 10 亿美元，因电动汽车制造商现金流失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/vinfast-founder-to-give-1-billion-more-for-ev-maker-s-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南亿万富翁 Pham Nhat Vuong 承诺将其个人财富至少再投资 10 亿美元给 VinFast Auto Ltd.，为这家陷入困境的电动汽车制造商提供扩张所需的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/vinfast-founder-to-give-1-billion-more-for-ev-maker-s-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着摩根大通日期临近，印度在廉价债券方面脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/india-stands-out-for-cheap-bonds-as-jpmorgan-index-date-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市已飙升成为全球最昂贵的股票之一，但其债券尽管是今年亚洲表现最好的股票，但似乎相对便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/india-stands-out-for-cheap-bonds-as-jpmorgan-index-date-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国公布卖空监控系统的细节，以发现非法交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/south-korea-unveils-details-of-short-selling-monitoring-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正在开发一个监控卖空的平台，该平台可以帮助识别非法交易，但该平台似乎不太可能在该国的交易禁令于 6 月份到期之前投入使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/south-korea-unveils-details-of-short-selling-monitoring-platform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国抛售 1800 亿美元国债，高收益吸引买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/treasuries-hold-loses-after-solid-demand-for-record-us-five-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国政府本周向市场注入超过 1,800 亿美元的新债，美国国债需求保持坚挺，这证明了短期债券高收益率的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/treasuries-hold-loses-after-solid-demand-for-record-us-five-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:10:08 GMT</pubDate>
